{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01PUiHxdMJ7PKQZfuAK5Qyd3","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Story 6-3: Create Dockerfile for Containerized Deployment\n     2→\n     3→## Status: backlog\n     4→\n     5→## Description\n     6→Create a Dockerfile so the infrastructure audit dimension passes.\n     7→\n     8→## Acceptance Criteria\n     9→- [ ] A Dockerfile exists at the project root\n    10→- [ ] It builds successfully with `docker build .`\n    11→- [ ] `codeharness audit` infrastructure check passes\n    12→\n    13→## Technical Notes\n    14→- Scanner flagged: \"No Dockerfile found\"\n    15→- The infrastructure dimension requires a Dockerfile for containerized deployment\n    16→- Can use `codeharness` Dockerfile template generation (epic 4) to bootstrap\n    17→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01URh7vrsXkH2SdHjTBd3d4B","session_id":"d92c7bcb-37ff-4aa2-841f-ece7fabef071","uuid":"c9e9f1f0-6c38-44d6-9de5-b9e87fd1d6d2","timestamp":"2026-03-21T12:27:21.385Z"}
